title: Elden Ring : Road To The Erdree Vol 2
author: Phil Christie
description: Aseo the Tarnished’s exploration of Stormveil Castle puts him on a collision course with the demigod Godrick the Grafted! Now they must face each other in a fierce…sculpture competition? Who will make the best impression with their most definitely serious and legitimate art skills―and why is Melina one of the judges?!
